---
layout: landing.njk
title: Cartographer | Ionrift Workshop
description: Describe an outdoor area and export a finished battle map. Cartographer early access is in preparation.
canonical: https://ionrift.cloud/cartographer/
ogTitle: Cartographer
ogDescription: Battle maps from a description. Early access in preparation.
bodyClass: page-cartographer
---

{% include "landing/nav.njk" %}

<main class="page-main module-detail page-cartographer">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="page-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
            <span>{{ cartographer.name }}</span>
        </nav>

        <header class="module-detail-header" style="--module-color: {{ cartographer.accent }};">
            <div class="module-detail-icon">
                <img src="{{ cartographer.icon }}" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="module-detail-intro">
                <span class="module-pill pill-ea">Early Access soon</span>
                <h1 class="module-detail-title">{{ cartographer.name }}</h1>
                <p class="module-detail-tag" style="color: {{ cartographer.accent }};">{{ cartographer.tagline }}</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="module-trailer">
            <div class="module-trailer-placeholder">
                <span>Preview coming with early access</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="module-detail-body ionrift-window">
            <p class="module-detail-desc">{{ cartographer.lead }}</p>

{% if cartographer.detailBody and cartographer.detailBody.length %}
            <div class="module-detail-copy">
{% for para in cartographer.detailBody %}
                <p>{{ para }}</p>
{% endfor %}
            </div>
{% endif %}

            <div class="module-detail-disclosure">
                <p>{{ cartographer.disclosure }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="module-detail-actions">
{% if cartographer.hostedAppUrl %}
                <a href="{{ cartographer.hostedAppUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary module-detail-cta">{{ cartographer.ctaLabel }}</a>
{% else %}
                <span class="btn btn-ghost module-detail-cta module-detail-cta--disabled">{{ cartographer.ctaLabel }}</span>
{% endif %}
                <a href="{{ cartographer.patreonUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-patreon module-detail-cta">See tiers on Patreon</a>
            </div>

{% if not cartographer.hostedAppUrl %}
            <p class="module-install-note">The hosted app link goes live with early access. Patreon subscribers will get access when it opens.</p>
{% endif %}
        </div>

        <p class="page-back">
            <a href="/#modules">&larr; All modules</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</main>

{% include "landing/footer.njk" %}
